Step 1: Download the 6 Files
Download these from the links above:

test-form.html
address-form.html
contact-form.html
server.py
test_mapper.py
TEST_FORM_README.md

Put them all in the same folder (e.g., test-form/)

Step 2: Start the Server
Open terminal in that folder and run:
bashpython server.py
```

You'll see:
```
ğŸš€ Test Form Server Starting...
ğŸ“ Server running at: http://localhost:8000
