Leave this terminal running!

Step 3: Test Your Solution
Option A: Use the Test Script (Automated)
Open a NEW terminal in the same folder:
bash# Set your API key
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY='your-key-here'

# Run the test
python test_mapper.py
This will automatically run your form mapper against the test form!

Option B: Use Your Own Code (Manual)
pythonfrom selenium import webdriver
from form_mapper_orchestrator import FormMapperOrchestrator
from ai_client_wrapper import AIClientWrapper

# Setup
driver = webdriver.Chrome()
driver.get("http://localhost:8000/test-form.html")  # â† This URL!

ai_client = AIClientWrapper(api_key="your-key", provider="claude")

# Map the form
orchestrator = FormMapperOrchestrator(driver, ai_client, "test_form")
result = orchestrator.start_mapping(max_iterations=30)

# Check results
print(f"Mapped {len(result['gui_fields'])} fields!")

driver.quit()
```

